      <title>埃克森美孚完成 600 億美元收購 Pioneer Natural 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/exxon-mobil-completes-60-billion-deal-pioneer-natural-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油和天然氣生產商埃克森美孚(Exxon Mobil) 週五表示，該公司已完成以600 億美元收購先鋒自然資源(Pioneer Natural Resources) 的交易，一天前該交易已獲得美國聯邦貿易委員會(FTC)的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/exxon-mobil-completes-60-billion-deal-pioneer-natural-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美國四月就業成長放緩；失業率升至3.9%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-growth-slows-april-unemployment-rate-rises-39-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國4月就業成長放緩幅度超過預期，年度薪資漲幅降溫，但由於勞動市場仍相當緊張，現在預計聯準會將在9月前開始降息可能還為時過早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-growth-slows-april-unemployment-rate-rises-39-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
